# Marker file: presence opts this project in to OMP's cwd-aware shim.
#
# The omp.cmd / omp shim in ~/.bun/bin checks for this file (among others)
# and, when found, sets PI_CODING_AGENT_DIR to this .omp/ directory so OMP
# loads models.yml, config.yml, themes/, tools/, commands/, prompts/,
# modules/, memories/, agent.db, history.db, and sessions/ from here instead
# of the global ~/.omp/agent.
#
# Delete this file to opt the project out without removing the rest of .omp/.
